## Third-party attributions

### Section 11 coaching framework
The Recovery Index (RI) and ACWR training load formulas used in the
`review_training` MCP tool are derived from the Section 11 coaching
framework by CrankAddict (https://github.com/CrankAddict/section-11).

MIT License — Copyright (c) CrankAddict

